<p><b>We explore a new era in bringing bigger and better online video to the whole enterprise, and here’s the best thing…it doesn’t choke your internal network! </b></p>

<p>Dinesh Kumar our resident expert in bringing the benefits of online video to the enterprise, talks to Reuben Bennett, Riverbed.  They discuss how through both Riverbed and Viostream technologies, large scale enterprises can advance and successfully implement enterprise wide video communications without choking their internal networks.</p>

